    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Drain your<strong> tofu</strong> and pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Crumble your <strong>tofu</strong> into small bite-sized pieces</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1639478082758-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
