          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1639478088896-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>tomato paste</strong> to the pan with the <strong>remaining soy sauce</strong> and 100ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [140ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[180ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Stir it all together and cook for 2-3 min or until thickened</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1639478092166-x200.jpg",
