            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Squeeze the pouch[es]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>of <strong>cooked white long grain rice</strong> to separate the grains</p><p>Add your<strong> cooked white long grain rice</strong> to the pan with the sweetcorn and a splash of <strong>water</strong> (if looking a little dry!)</p><p>Stir everything together and cook for 3-4 min or until the rice has warmed through – this is your <strong>spiced rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1639478094382-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1639478094382-x400.jpg",
