          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1639478094382-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dice your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> finely</p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Cut your<strong> lime[s] </strong>into 1 wedge per person</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1639478097764-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1639478097764-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1639478097764-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1639478097764-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1639478097764-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> spiced rice </strong>in a bowl topped with the <strong>crispy tofu</strong> – this is your <strong>spicy tofu sofritas bowl</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>chopped tomato</strong>, <strong>chopped coriander</strong>, the juice of <strong>half</strong> your<strong> lime wedges </strong>and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Season with a grind of<strong> pepper </strong>and garnish with the <strong>remaining chilli flakes</strong> <strong> </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) and a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
